<script>
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {
            document.querySelectorAll('[data-toggle="collapse"]').forEach(function (trigger) {
                trigger.addEventListener('click', function (event) {
                    event.preventDefault();
                    const targetId = trigger.getAttribute('href') || trigger.getAttribute('data-target');
                    if (!targetId) return;
                    const target = document.querySelector(targetId.startsWith('#') ? targetId : `#${targetId}`);
                    if (!target) return;
                    target.classList.toggle('show');
                    const parentLi = trigger.closest('li');
                    if (parentLi) {
                        parentLi.classList.toggle('active', target.classList.contains('show'));
                    }
                });
            });
        });
    </script>
